OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day and mostly cloudy
OL,6,Fnear the coasts with some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. Further inland will
OL,8,Fsee clearer skies and plenty of
OL,9,Fsunshine, feeling warm here.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with late
OL,12,Fevening sunshine for many but cloudier
OL,13,Fin the west near the coast. Dry with
OL,14,Fclear intervals overnight, staying
OL,15,Fmostly cloudy in the west.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAnother dry day with long
OL,18,Fsunny spells away from western coasts,
OL,19,Fwhich remain rather cloudy. Feeling
OL,20,Fwarm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
